Package jsx.ui.dd.event

Drag-and-drop event objects and their handlers.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
OnDragMove Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragMove type.
OnDragOut Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragOut type.
OnDragOver Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragOver type.
OnDragStart Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragStart type.
OnDragStop Declares an interface for high level event listeners that handle events of the DragStop type.
 

Class Summary
DragMove A type of high level events that may be fired from a source widget when the browser mouse dragging-move event occurs on the element wrapped by the widget.
DragOut A type of high level events that may be fired from a dragged widget when the mouse moves out a related component while dragging the source widget.
DragOver A type of high level events that may be fired from a dragged widget when the mouse moves over a related widget while dragging the source widget.
DragStart A type of high level events that may be fired from a source widget when the widget is being dragged.
DragStop A type of high level events that may be fired from a dragged widget when the mouse is released.
